1f19209278f7feaee27a8211f11851c3fe601e5a5c548c8b1bcf1aae7e17c0fe2933e07a3b5b38115c940949ca4c30ad669c618bad69fe2b3d8d1a4d91fecc1b  10-consolidate-lib-dirs.patch"
